{"word":"G3140 - μαρτυρέω - martyréō - mar-too-reh'-o - Charge","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μαρτυρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">martyréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mar-too-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Charge</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சாட்சிகளாயிரு, சாட்சிகொடு, சாட்சிசொல், சாட்சியாக அறிவி"},{"paragraph":"to be a witness, to bear witness, testify"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3144 - μάρτυς - mártys - mar'-toos/3144\">G3144</a>; to <i>be a witness</i>, that is, <i>testify</i> (literally or figuratively): - charge, give [evidence], bear record, have (obtain, of) good (honest) report, be well reported of, testify, give (have) testimony, (be, bear, give, obtain) witness.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1263/1263\">G1263</a>, <a href=\"#/G1957/1957\">G1957</a>, <a href=\"#/G2649/2649\">G2649</a>, <a href=\"#/G3140/3140\">G3140</a>, <a href=\"#/G3141/3141\">G3141</a>, <a href=\"#/G3142/3142\">G3142</a>, <a href=\"#/G3143/3143\">G3143</a>, <a href=\"#/G3144/3144\">G3144</a>, <a href=\"#/G4303/4303\">G4303</a>, <a href=\"#/G4828/4828\">G4828</a>, <a href=\"#/G4901/4901\">G4901</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575/5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576/5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577/5577\">G5577</a>"}]}